<section class="hero">

<h1>
Pathway <span>Analysis</span>
</h1>

<p>
Pathway analysis interprets metabolite changes through biochemical pathways, helping researchers understand metabolic regulation, disease mechanisms, pathway disruption, and systems-level biological function.
</p>

<div class="hero-image">
  <img
    src="/research-pathway-analysis-hero-v1.png"
